Package com.graphql_java_generator.client

Interface GraphQLMutationExecutor

public interface GraphQLMutationExecutor
This interface marks a class as being the non reactive executor for a GraphQL mutation. This is allows Spring to inject the executor for the mutation type (if any) into an autowired attribute of a Spring Bean.
